import Title from "./component/Title"
    import {Navbar} from "react-bootstrap"

    const SubNavbar = () => {

        return  <>

                <Navbar bg="primary" variant="dark" className="mt-5 w-50 mx-auto">

                <Navbar.Brand href="#home">
                    <Title></Title>
                </Navbar.Brand>

                <Nav className="ms-auto">

<Dropdown>

    <Dropdown.Toggle className="btn btn-light nav-link dropdown-toggle text-dark header-btn-lang" id="dropdown-basic">
            שפה
    </Dropdown.Toggle>

    <Dropdown.Menu>

        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">עברית</Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">אנגלית</Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">רוסית</Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">עברית</Dropdown.Item>

    </Dropdown.Menu>

 </Dropdown>

{ ! isUserLoggedIn &&

    <Nav.Link href="/login">
        <Button type="button" className="btn btn-light btn-lg header-btn-login">כניסה</Button>
    </Nav.Link>
}

{ isUserLoggedIn &&

    <Nav.Link href="/search/match">
        <Button type="button" className="btn btn-light btn-lg header-btn-login">חפש התאמה</Button>
    </Nav.Link>
}

{ isUserLoggedIn &&

    <Nav.Link href="/profile">
        <Button type="button" className="btn btn-light btn-lg ">פרופיל</Button>
    </Nav.Link>
}



</Nav>

                </Navbar>

                </>
     }

     export default SubNavbar
